		<p class='mb-6 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400'>
			Seasoned Technical Manager with 15+ years of proven expertise in leading IT infrastructure teams, designing cloud solutions, and driving digital transformation. Demonstrated success in managing complex enterprise systems, implementing robust security frameworks, and delivering innovative technology solutions that drive business growth.
		</p>
	</div>
	
	<div class='relative max-w-4xl mx-auto'>
		<!-- Main vertical line with gradient effect -->
		<div class='absolute left-6 sm:left-1/2 w-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-400 via-purple-400 to-green-400 h-full timeline-line'></div>

		<div class='space-y-6 sm:space-y-8'>
			{
				experiences.map((exp, idx) => {
					return (
						<div class={`relative flex items-start sm:items-center experience-card rounded-xl p-4 transition-all duration-300 ${idx % 2 === 0 ? 'bg-white/50 dark:bg-zinc-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm' : 'bg-white/30 dark:bg-zinc-800/30 backdrop-blur-sm'}`}>
